00:04:27.710 --> 00:04:31.040 align:middle line:84%
>> So it's exciting to see
this physiological biomarker

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:35.690 align:middle line:84%
changing in association
with reduced PTSD symptoms.

00:04:35.690 --> 00:04:38.540 align:middle line:84%
And it makes sense because
of the relationship

00:04:38.540 --> 00:04:40.790 align:middle line:84%
