nervous system.

00:04:40.790 --> 00:04:44.630 align:middle line:84%
And it's very exciting
and has huge implications

00:04:44.630 --> 00:04:47.600 align:middle line:84%
for the treatment of PTSD and
other mental illnesses that

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.400 align:middle line:90%
are difficult to treat.

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:52.160 align:middle line:84%
But the fact that we found
out for the first time

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:57.230 align:middle line:84%
evidence of this physiological
biomarker changing in relation

00:04:57.230 --> 00:05:02.750 align:middle line:84%
to the healing lucid dream has
implications for illnesses that

00:05:02.750 --> 00:05:04.280 align:middle line:90%
are more physically manifested.

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:07.280 align:middle line:84%
If you can change the level
of enzyme in your body

00:05:07.280 --> 00:05:09.860 align:middle line:84%
through a healing
lucid dream, that

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:14.150 align:middle line:84%
means you can change physical
illnesses, which I think

00:05:14.150 --> 00:05:15.590 align:middle line:90%
is tremendous.

00:05:15.590 --> 00:05:18.920 align:middle line:84%
And we have the opportunity to
learn a lot about the healing

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:20.360 align:middle line:90%
power of the mind.

